message.content:
actually what we need to add is the following:

  "hooks": {
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "~/.claude/hooks/reminders/response-tracker.sh init \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\""
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "UserPromptSubmit": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "~/.claude/hooks/reminders/response-tracker.sh track \"$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR\""
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },

but for when we're modifying the project-level settings.json or settings.local.json, the command should start with $CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/... (not ~/.claude/...)

